room_title: Escape room "The Bunker" by Fox in a Box Chicago in Chicago
room_address: 47 W Polk Street, Ste L5 Chicago, IL 60605
room_description: Your special agents' team has the hardest task yet ahead of you. Travel back in time to the years of Cold War between USSR and USA. A double agent wants to start the nuclear war. Find yourselves trapped in an underground bunker where the missile launch codes will start a nuclear war in 60 minutes. You have to abort the mission, whatever it takes.
